name: Taman Mumbul Sangeh
address: Jl. Brahmana No.38, Sangeh, Kec. Abiansemal, Kabupaten Badung, Bali 80352, Indonesia
review 1: Very nice and quiet place but I have been scammed in the entrance to pay 20k in the entrance by the guard/parking guy. More you stay in Indonesia, more you lose your respect and trust to people.
review 2:
5 star. This is holy place despite everything you fell. If you are being scammed or paying more money than needed that another problem and not the place problems its people problem.

Repurification for your soul
review 3:
Beautiful spot with a large lake, filled with fish and a temple at the far end.  Across the road were more lakes and a holy bath: sort of like Empul Pura Tirta but without the tourists.

You can buy fish food - 5K for 2 bags and feed the large, hungry fish
review 4:
The place is nothing special.
Turist place..
It's a quiet place with some fish
That's it.
And then you can shower in some "holy" water.
review 5: Good place but nothing extraordinary to oay the entrance fees, you can skip it or take pictures from outside like i did

name: OYO 92438 Nugraha Stay
address: 80352 Batulumbang, Gerana, Badung, Sangeh, Abiansemal, Bali, 80352, Indonesia
review 1: Good hotel and good family staff. Room whit A/C and clean. I like because is a quiet place and far from ubud traffic. To get this hotel you need rent a bike becuase is far from center. Is perfect if tou want live a local experience in bali. Thanks for all
review 2:
Dirty, the manager or owner try to make me pay more than the price and then take on my card, nothing of the stuff right on internet, full of insect !
the staff amazing and nice though
review 3:
The hotel is out of nowhere. We were denied the room we booked, they said its fully booked and gave us a room wr i guess his friends where staying!!! The room stinks of cigarette, unhygienic. No internet, no hot water.
highly unhygienic.
Don't go here if you are looking for a pleasant vacation.
The only plus point is you can enjoy the country side ride which you probably can do anyways if you rent a vehicle in city.
review 4: booked this place for my driver & this was an empty house.  couldn't believe that this property listed in OYO.  the property location is at the end of the road, in the middle of nowhere in the jungle.
review 5: THE OWNER IS A THIEF, NEVER COME HERE
